  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\((\\Omega, \\mathcal{T},\n\\prob)\\)</span> un espace probabilisé et deux événements <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(B\\)</span>. On note <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\overline{A}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\overline{B}\\)</span> les événements\ncomplémentaires de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(B\\)</span>.</p>\n<p>On sait que : <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\prob(A) = \\frac{1}{2}\n\\quad , \\quad \\prob(A \\cup B) = \\frac{7}{8} \\quad , \\quad\n\\prob(\\overline{B}) = \\frac{3}{8}\\]</span></p>\n<p>Calculer les probabilités suivantes :</p>\n<ol>\n<li></li>\n<li></li>\n<li></li>\n<li></li>\n</ol>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(A \\cap B)\\)</span> ;</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(A \\cap B) =\n\\frac{2}{8}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cap\n\\overline{B})\\)</span> ;</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cap \\overline{B}) =\n\\frac{1}{8}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cup\n\\overline{B})\\)</span> ;</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cup \\overline{B}) =\n\\frac{6}{8}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cup B)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(\\overline{A} \\cup B) =\n\\frac{3}{8}\\)</span></p>\n"
    }
  ]
}